ios are potentially relevant both for the gas-giant satellites in the\nSolar system and for the dynamical evolution of exomoons.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Jul 2014 20:00:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-07-11"}
