ications to real\nseismicity are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Jul 2014 05:10:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Aug 2015 05:21:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-28"}
