nts; however, a cyclic evolution emerges for some\n(but not all) areas over long timescales.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Jul 2014 15:40:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Mar 2015 10:59:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-11"}
